sequenceDiagram
    participant Scheduler
    participant Agent
    participant Advisory
    participant WeatherForecast
    participant RainHistory
    participant Irrigation

    Note over Scheduler,Irrigation: Step 1 — Generate advice (06:00)
    Scheduler->>Agent: generateDailyAdvice (cron)
    Agent->>Advisory: calculateAndProposeAdvice(today)
    Advisory->>WeatherForecast: getForecast(today)
    WeatherForecast-->>Advisory: WeatherForecast
    Advisory->>RainHistory: updateRainHistory(7 days)
    RainHistory-->>Advisory: List<RainHistory>
    Advisory->>Irrigation: getEvents()
    Irrigation-->>Advisory: List<IrrigationEvent>
    Advisory->>Advisory: Evaluate irrigation rules
    Advisory->>Advisory: Save advice (PENDING)
    Advisory->>Advisory: Publish IrrigationProposed event

    Note over Scheduler,Irrigation: Step 2 — Execute advice (07:30)
    Scheduler->>Agent: executeDailyAdvice (cron)
    Agent->>Advisory: getTodayAdvice()
    Advisory-->>Agent: IrrigationAdvice
    alt durationMinutes > 0
        Agent->>Irrigation: startIrrigation(minutes)
        Irrigation->>Irrigation: Save IrrigationEvent (COMPLETED)
        Agent->>Advisory: saveAdvice(EXECUTED)
    end
